content: Does someone have an example IPS in sushi format (FSH)?
@John Moehrke You can find that in the 'connectathon' branch (it doesn't exactly match what's in 'connectathon-2', but it's definitely an example).
excellent. I think we need an example of what we are after before we profile it. so starting with a example IPS, allows us to adjust it. -- @ANDREA FOURQUET
note that the composition in there is not marked as compliant with IPS... but, it served my purpose of getting started.
